要求设计一个calendar system。要求1000用户，并可能拓展到100M+

http://www.1point3acres.com/bbs/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=175497#pid2272026
canlendar design
几个主要功能，添加修改删除event，邀请别人，看别人的availability。
然后跟server怎么交互，数据怎么load，数据库schema设计等等。
说完功能考量scalability，都常规的design题步骤走一下.

1. what functions does calendar system provide ?
query/add/update/delete event

2. can user see different date range of calendar, or always display one month
calendar view ?
Yearly view, monthly view, weekly view, daily view. or custom range

3. can user send invitation to other users ?

4. Does it provide notification function ? notify by email/txt

5. Can the calendar event be repeat, like it happens every week,
or every month ?

6. holiday/birthday mark

7. can calendar be shared with other users ?

8. re-occurring event

Zookeeper,Kafka,cassandra

http://massivetechinterview.blogspot.com/2015/10/google-calendar-architecture.html